snippet.title: STEEL ASSAULT: Steam Trailer
snippet.description:
Wishlist on Steam here: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1280300/Steel_Assault/

Punch, whip, and zipline your way through a post-apocalyptic America in this retro-style action platformer! Play as Taro Takahashi, a resistance soldier on a revenge mission against the dictator who lords over the ashes. Welcome to the world of STEEL ASSAULT!
